-- Target shareholder CtW Investment wants separate CEO, chairman 
-- By Jim Finkle
-- Mon May 05, 2014 03:13PM EDT
-- None



BOSTON, May 5 (Reuters) - Target Corp <TGT.N> shareholder CtW Investment Group called on the retailer to separate the roles of chairman and chief executive after Monday's announcement that Chief Executive and Chairman Gregg Steinhafel is leaving the company.

